OL,3,CWife of former rugby star Scott
OL,4,CHastings missing after wild swim
OL,6,FJenny Hastings, the wife of former
OL,7,FScottish rugby international Scott
OL,8,FHastings, has been missing since
OL,9,FTuesday after she went for a wild swim
OL,10,Fin the Firth of Forth.
OL,12,FHer family said Jenny failed to return
OL,13,Fafter swimming in Wardie Bay in
OL,14,FEdinburgh.
OL,16,FIn a statement, the Hastings family
OL,17,Fsaid they were "absolutely
OL,18,Fheartbroken" at the news, adding that
OL,19,FJenny had "struggled with her mental
OL,20,Fhealth for a number of years".
