OL,6,FIt added: "We miss our Jenny. She
OL,7,Fleaves a gaping hole in all our hearts
OL,8,Fand hope that she is returned to us
OL,9,Fsafely so that we can celebrate her
OL,10,Fremarkable life."
OL,12,FThe Maritime and Coastguard Agency
OL,13,Fsaid they received a "report of
OL,14,Fconcern" at about 2.45pm, and a
OL,15,Fhelicopter, coastguard rescue teams,
OL,16,Flifeboats and other nearby vessels all
OL,17,Ftook part in a search.
OL,19,FHowever the agency said the search
OL,20,Ffailed to find anything, and was
OL,21,Fcalled off at 8.20pm that evening.
