OL,6,FThe family confirmed the case is being
OL,7,Ftreated by the police as a "high risk
OL,8,Fmissing person case".
OL,10,FIn the statement, the family requested
OL,11,Ftime to "grieve privately with family
OL,12,Fmember" and said they will share any
OL,13,Fupdates when they hear from police.
OL,15,FIt is signed "Scott, Corey, Daniel,
OL,16,FKerry-Anne & Ian".
OL,18,FScott Hastings - brother of former
OL,19,FScotland captain Gavin Hastings - was
OL,20,Falso a Scottish international and
OL,21,Fplayed from 1986 to 1997.
